1
00:00:12,210 --> 00:00:18,410
[2009]

2
00:00:13,800 --> 00:00:14,400
Chuan.

3
00:00:15,880 --> 00:00:16,480
Chuan.

4
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:19,760
Yan Bin invited us to his house
for dinner tonight.

5
00:00:20,670 --> 00:00:21,280
Chuan!

6
00:00:23,160 --> 00:00:24,160
Chuan!

7
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:26,070
Chuan!

8
00:00:36,150 --> 00:00:37,410
You little crazy girl.

9
00:00:37,560 --> 00:00:38,840
You're going too far.

10
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:40,820
Wearing earplugs wasn't enough—

11
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:42,280
now you're taping them shut?

12
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:43,580
Am I really that annoying?

13
00:00:43,580 --> 00:00:45,190
Well, you chirp non-stop
as soon as you get home.

14
00:00:45,190 --> 00:00:47,120
Don't I have to protect my hearing?

15
00:00:47,160 --> 00:00:48,600
Is your hearing more important or am I?

16
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:49,520
Oh, spare me.

17
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:51,200
For such a freebie question,

18
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,260
go ask Jiang Cheng.

19
00:00:56,110 --> 00:00:57,600
As a sniper,

20
00:00:57,920 --> 00:01:00,030
ears are as important as eyes.

21
00:01:00,430 --> 00:01:01,170
Okay, okay.

22
00:01:01,200 --> 00:01:02,090
I'll tape it up for you.

23
00:01:02,090 --> 00:01:03,620
Seal it tight. Tape it well.

24
00:01:04,069 --> 00:01:04,790
You can't hear now, right?

25
00:01:04,790 --> 00:01:05,650
You can't hear.

26
00:01:06,630 --> 00:01:07,230
Chuan,

27
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,310
you really are a big fool.

28
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:11,230
A big idiot.

29
00:01:11,710 --> 00:01:13,170
You're really something.

30
00:01:24,039 --> 00:01:24,789
Chuan,

31
00:01:25,070 --> 00:01:26,840
are current anti-sniper detection devices

32
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:28,500
already very well developed?

33
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,560
Theoretically,

34
00:01:30,870 --> 00:01:31,920
as long as you fire a shot,

35
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:33,690
your position can be quickly locked onto.

36
00:01:33,690 --> 00:01:36,280
You might not even have the chance
to fire a second shot.

37
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:36,870
Chuan,

38
00:01:37,240 --> 00:01:39,770
isn't it very dangerous
for you to be a sniper?

39
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:41,130
I think

40
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:42,360
current devices

41
00:01:42,380 --> 00:01:43,910
cannot replace human ears.

42
00:01:44,600 --> 00:01:45,330
Dad is right.

43
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,440
Situations on the battlefield
are ever-changing.

44
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,350
Having a good pair of ears

45
00:01:48,350 --> 00:01:50,150
is the best anti-sniper system.

46
00:01:52,229 --> 00:01:52,920
Chuan,

47
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,680
your new sniper rifle...

48
00:01:55,509 --> 00:01:56,710
Are you done?

49
00:01:57,330 --> 00:01:59,530
How about you four cops living together

50
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,920
in the future?

51
00:02:02,340 --> 00:02:03,090
Mom!

52
00:02:04,220 --> 00:02:04,810
Mom.

53
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:06,500
Your cooking is so delicious.

54
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,970
It's so delicious, Mom.

55
00:02:07,970 --> 00:02:08,560
It's very tasty.

56
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:09,560
Let's talk about something else.

57
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:11,020
Then that sniper rifle...

58
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:39,500
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

59
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:42,250
[Episode 14]

60
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,970
Before the Jingang operation,

61
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:47,079
Leader Yao once confided in me.

62
00:03:48,079 --> 00:03:49,810
There's an undercover officer

63
00:03:50,410 --> 00:03:52,280
inside Old Scorpion's
criminal organization—

64
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,750
codename "Cangfeng."

65
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,980
I had a single-line contact
with him before.

66
00:03:57,900 --> 00:03:58,690
Cangfeng?

67
00:04:00,310 --> 00:04:01,360
So this time,

68
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,140
the trade at Jingang Wharf

69
00:04:03,490 --> 00:04:05,640
was intel sent back by Cangfeng.

70
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,440
From the current situation,

71
00:04:08,710 --> 00:04:10,830
he might have been exposed
a long time ago.

72
00:04:10,830 --> 00:04:11,590
So this time,

73
00:04:11,650 --> 00:04:12,560
the rescue

74
00:04:12,700 --> 00:04:14,160
isn't just for Leader Yao—

75
00:04:14,510 --> 00:04:15,840
it's also for Cangfeng.

76
00:04:16,560 --> 00:04:17,430
Cangfeng?

77
00:04:17,589 --> 00:04:18,990
Is it possible that he...

78
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:20,829
Bad news!

79
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,160
What's wrong?

80
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:24,310
Two male bodies were found
in the eastern suburbs.

81
00:04:24,310 --> 00:04:25,240
One of them

82
00:04:25,340 --> 00:04:26,740
might be Team Leader Yao.

83
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:44,680
Professor Jiang.

84
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,360
Senior.

85
00:04:45,390 --> 00:04:46,500
How's the situation?

86
00:04:46,500 --> 00:04:47,720
The investigation is basically done.

87
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,310
We were waiting for you
to come take a look.

88
00:04:49,310 --> 00:04:51,420
The two bodies were discovered
by a local resident

89
00:04:51,420 --> 00:04:52,159
while collecting seafood along the shore.

90
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:54,190
The forensic doctor's preliminary judgment
is that they were shot at close range,

91
00:04:54,190 --> 00:04:55,390
then tied together

92
00:04:55,390 --> 00:04:56,180
and dumped here.

93
00:04:56,180 --> 00:04:57,480
A handgun was found at the scene,

94
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,620
and fingerprints have been lifted

95
00:04:58,620 --> 00:05:00,560
and sent back to the station for analysis.

96
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:02,120
So far, only one identity
has been confirmed—

97
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,270
Leader Yao Weihai.

98
00:05:03,570 --> 00:05:04,970
What about the other one?

99
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,460
It can't be confirmed yet.

100
00:05:07,010 --> 00:05:08,020
Where is the gunshot wound?

101
00:05:08,020 --> 00:05:09,150
The back of the head.

102
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,050
Leader.

103
00:05:59,070 --> 00:05:59,470
Okay.

104
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:06,200
This way, please.

105
00:06:08,110 --> 00:06:08,660
Mr. Wan.

106
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:09,890
Mr. Wan.

107
00:06:11,430 --> 00:06:12,360
What's going on?

108
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,880
I saw you earlier this morning,

109
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,610
and you brought them along too.

110
00:06:16,190 --> 00:06:17,920
The Jingang operation failed.

111
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:20,700
The higher-ups have sent
an investigation team down.

112
00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:21,900
Be careful recently,

113
00:06:22,450 --> 00:06:23,490
but don't stress—

114
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:26,500
just stay calm.
It's nothing to panic about.

115
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:29,160
After Leader Yao went missing,

116
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:32,210
I immediately launched a rescue operation.

117
00:06:33,250 --> 00:06:34,200
Normally,

118
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:35,930
when criminals

119
00:06:36,260 --> 00:06:37,520
take a police officer,

120
00:06:37,630 --> 00:06:39,360
it's to use them as leverage

121
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:42,630
to negotiate with higher authorities.

122
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,600
So at first,

123
00:06:44,909 --> 00:06:46,770
I still held onto a sliver of hope,

124
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,600
waiting for their call.

125
00:06:49,870 --> 00:06:50,830
But later,

126
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:53,210
Professor Jiang

127
00:06:53,850 --> 00:06:55,710
came up with a more accurate idea.

128
00:06:56,190 --> 00:06:58,650
I thought the target
was Leader Yao himself.

129
00:06:59,210 --> 00:07:00,870
Let's just call it intuition.

130
00:07:02,710 --> 00:07:04,910
That's what I told Chief Tan at the time.

131
00:07:04,980 --> 00:07:06,440
The time limit is 48 hours.

132
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,630
If we couldn't rescue him

133
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:10,160
within 48 hours,

134
00:07:10,970 --> 00:07:13,230
then Leader Yao and his undercover agent

135
00:07:13,530 --> 00:07:15,190
would both be in grave danger.

136
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:18,540
Before the operation, Leader Yao

137
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:20,520
also knew there were huge risks.

138
00:07:20,890 --> 00:07:22,260
I can understand why Leader Yao

139
00:07:22,260 --> 00:07:23,860
didn't want to retreat then.

140
00:07:24,110 --> 00:07:26,090
Once everything was set in motion,
it was hard to pull back.

141
00:07:26,090 --> 00:07:28,090
When we first planned the takedown,

142
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,720
we were cautious,

143
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:32,050
but we also had high expectations.

144
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,800
Leader Yao and I

145
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:36,260
verified the vessel information together,

146
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,800
and at that time, the intel

147
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,860
was very accurate.

148
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:43,270
After Chief Tan finished his call
with Leader Yao,

149
00:07:43,270 --> 00:07:44,480
we didn't waste a second

150
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,280
and moved in to provide support.

151
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:48,000
We regrouped with Wan

152
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,270
to capture He Wu.

153
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:50,430
No one expected

154
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:52,600
that Old Scorpion
would be right there with them.

155
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:54,040
This is completely different

156
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,970
from what we knew at the beginning.

157
00:07:57,210 --> 00:07:58,800
The news we got at first was

158
00:07:58,830 --> 00:08:00,870
that Old Scorpion
would appear at the pier.

159
00:08:00,870 --> 00:08:02,480
So when something happened to Leader Yao,

160
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,610
I initially thought

161
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,510
he met Old Scorpion at the pier.

162
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:07,570
Later I figured out what was going on.

163
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,560
I was shot by a sniper at the time

164
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:10,530
and got injured,

165
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:12,750
so I didn't participate in
the subsequent pursuit.

166
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:14,310
Fortunately, Zhou Jin reacted quickly

167
00:08:14,310 --> 00:08:15,440
and dragged me back.

168
00:08:16,190 --> 00:08:18,250
Otherwise, I would have been killed.

169
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:21,280
When Leader Yao was ambushed,
there was a lot of smoke.

170
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:22,540
The scene was chaotic.

171
00:08:22,930 --> 00:08:23,950
Our surveillance system

172
00:08:23,950 --> 00:08:25,550
lost its picture for a while.

173
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,400
Although it wasn't long,

174
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,290
we didn't see

175
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,880
the critical process

176
00:08:29,910 --> 00:08:31,640
of Leader Yao being taken away.

177
00:08:31,830 --> 00:08:33,260
All the situations were reported

178
00:08:33,260 --> 00:08:34,990
by the front-line action team.

179
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:38,080
At the moment of the explosion, Leader Yao

180
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,840
was dragged into the underground tunnel.

181
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:40,539
We killed

182
00:08:40,570 --> 00:08:43,169
the 4 criminals
covering the tunnel entrance.

183
00:08:44,150 --> 00:08:45,510
They detonated the bomb

184
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:47,370
in the underground tunnel again,

185
00:08:47,790 --> 00:08:49,550
causing our action team members

186
00:08:49,550 --> 00:08:51,010
to almost be buried alive.

187
00:08:52,510 --> 00:08:53,510
A total of 6 people

188
00:08:54,270 --> 00:08:56,330
were injured in the whole operation.

189
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,360
There is also a

190
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:00,630
policewoman who had a direct encounter

191
00:09:00,630 --> 00:09:02,480
with the enemy sniper.

192
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,510
At that time, we already knew

193
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:06,840
Leader Yao was missing.

194
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,720
What I was thinking about

195
00:09:08,910 --> 00:09:10,670
was how to hold off the gang

196
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,970
and wait for backup.

197
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,680
We were outnumbered.

198
00:09:13,750 --> 00:09:15,240
The sniper took a shot from concealment,

199
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,480
which caused someone on our side

200
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,810
to get injured quickly.

201
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:19,230
I had made a judgment.

202
00:09:19,390 --> 00:09:20,960
If we kept dragging it out like this,

203
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:21,960
it was very likely

204
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:24,550
to turn into a situation
where they use the injured
to ambush our backup.

205
00:09:24,550 --> 00:09:26,270
It was very disadvantageous for us.

206
00:09:26,270 --> 00:09:27,930
My brother used to be a sniper.

207
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,800
He taught me how to locate by listening.

208
00:09:31,180 --> 00:09:33,510
I was somewhat confident I could find him.

209
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:35,750
Then

210
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,510
why did you go alone?

211
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:40,610
The fight had already broken out.

212
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:43,030
A frontal assault required more manpower.

213
00:09:43,510 --> 00:09:45,000
Under those circumstances,

214
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,260
I had to be the one to go.

215
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:47,790
And my position was good.

216
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:50,150
Going alone made me a small target,

217
00:09:50,150 --> 00:09:51,750
making it hard to be spotted.

218
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,550
But it did worry the team.

219
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:58,980
As one of the officers
injured on the front line,

220
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,960
where do you think

221
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,670
the biggest problem

222
00:10:02,670 --> 00:10:04,730
in the command of this operation lay?

223
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:07,100
Getting injured was my own fault.

224
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:08,240
Okay.

225
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:09,800
Your part ends here.

226
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:10,840
You can go back.

227
00:10:15,370 --> 00:10:15,840
What?

228
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:18,340
You have something to say?

229
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:20,980
Just one thing.

230
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:24,080
Please trust Chief Tan,

231
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,670
and Nancheng Branch.

232
00:10:25,910 --> 00:10:27,030
No one

233
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:29,370
wants to solve the case more than we do.

234
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:40,060
That won't do.

235
00:10:40,990 --> 00:10:42,540
You are the person in charge,

236
00:10:42,540 --> 00:10:43,640
the leader of the task force.

237
00:10:43,640 --> 00:10:45,700
How can you make the arrest yourself?

238
00:10:46,130 --> 00:10:47,250
Cangfeng

239
00:10:48,010 --> 00:10:49,250
is still inside.

240
00:10:50,790 --> 00:10:52,520
Only I can coordinate with him.

241
00:10:52,620 --> 00:10:55,360
Provincial Bureau
leaders will come to supervise.

242
00:10:55,360 --> 00:10:56,820
You'll be responsible for

243
00:10:56,850 --> 00:10:58,850
the overall command

244
00:10:59,510 --> 00:11:01,020
and coordination of this operation.

245
00:11:01,020 --> 00:11:01,690
Tan,

246
00:11:02,580 --> 00:11:03,300
please.

247
00:11:11,550 --> 00:11:12,200
Look.

248
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:15,170
His fatal wound is a shot
to the left chest

249
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,480
that went straight through the heart.

250
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:19,280
Leader Yao's situation
is much more complicated.

251
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:22,240
There are traces of
a cyanide capsule in his teeth.

252
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,150
It's hard to determine

253
00:11:24,320 --> 00:11:26,480
whether he bit it himself

254
00:11:26,580 --> 00:11:28,750
or if it broke accidentally
during the struggle,

255
00:11:28,750 --> 00:11:31,660
especially since he was also shot
in the back of the head around the same time.

256
00:11:31,660 --> 00:11:33,300
The trajectory is from top to bottom

257
00:11:33,300 --> 00:11:34,780
at a 45-degree angle.

258
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,200
Just like Cheng.

259
00:11:38,160 --> 00:11:40,190
Didn't we also find a gun?

260
00:11:40,540 --> 00:11:41,950
After comparative testing,

261
00:11:41,950 --> 00:11:43,150
the bullet in the head

262
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:44,200
was fired

263
00:11:44,220 --> 00:11:45,340
from

264
00:11:45,370 --> 00:11:46,170
this gun.

265
00:11:47,790 --> 00:11:48,660
Leaving the murder weapon

266
00:11:48,660 --> 00:11:50,020
at the dumping site...

267
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,510
It's another provocation.

268
00:11:52,510 --> 00:11:53,480
Not only that,

269
00:11:53,610 --> 00:11:54,920
we also found

270
00:11:55,050 --> 00:11:56,380
a set of fingerprints

271
00:11:56,550 --> 00:11:57,430
on this gun.

272
00:11:58,630 --> 00:11:59,510
Fingerprints?

273
00:12:04,000 --> 00:12:04,750
Chief Tan.

274
00:12:04,970 --> 00:12:05,600
Zhou Jin,

275
00:12:05,910 --> 00:12:07,310
come to my office right now.

276
00:12:07,310 --> 00:12:07,920
Yes.

277
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:11,900
I'll go see Chief Tan first.

278
00:12:11,900 --> 00:12:12,460
You go ahead.

279
00:12:12,460 --> 00:12:13,320
I'll stay here.

280
00:12:22,750 --> 00:12:25,010
I want to take a look at
Leader Yao's body.

281
00:12:27,790 --> 00:12:28,510
Come in.

282
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:38,260
Sir.

283
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:51,400
Zhou Jin,

284
00:12:53,550 --> 00:12:54,810
you are my apprentice,

285
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:59,380
and Zhou Chuan's biological sister.

286
00:13:01,090 --> 00:13:02,060
I trust you.

287
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:04,960
I also believe

288
00:13:06,420 --> 00:13:08,230
you are the most eager to see

289
00:13:09,510 --> 00:13:10,300
the 8.17 Case

290
00:13:11,020 --> 00:13:12,500
solved, right?

291
00:13:19,550 --> 00:13:20,240
Sir,

292
00:13:21,950 --> 00:13:22,750
what's wrong?

293
00:13:26,390 --> 00:13:27,390
I suspect

294
00:13:28,470 --> 00:13:30,070
we have a mole in our team.

295
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:38,840
Leader Yao

296
00:13:39,290 --> 00:13:41,350
was only recently transferred back,

297
00:13:41,730 --> 00:13:42,540
and this time

298
00:13:43,090 --> 00:13:44,890
he will personally lead the team

299
00:13:45,070 --> 00:13:46,280
to Jingang Wharf.

300
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,850
Only insiders know about this.

301
00:13:50,790 --> 00:13:51,700
But obviously,

302
00:13:52,410 --> 00:13:54,200
they were after Leader Yao.

303
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,280
How could they

304
00:13:57,350 --> 00:13:59,110
know our arrangement so well?

305
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:02,000
Do you have any suspects?

306
00:14:03,640 --> 00:14:04,880
I can't be sure yet.

307
00:14:06,800 --> 00:14:08,260
I need to think it through.

308
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:10,720
You and Professor Jiang

309
00:14:10,860 --> 00:14:11,740
must stay alert

310
00:14:13,820 --> 00:14:15,300
and watch your own safety.

311
00:14:19,010 --> 00:14:19,720
Got it.

312
00:14:21,580 --> 00:14:23,310
I didn't call you here for this.

313
00:14:26,550 --> 00:14:28,610
There are two more important things.

314
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:33,240
The identity of the other victim

315
00:14:33,310 --> 00:14:34,440
has been confirmed.

316
00:14:38,910 --> 00:14:40,310
His name is Meng Junfeng.

317
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:41,900
The file shows that

318
00:14:42,400 --> 00:14:43,600
during the 8.17 Case,

319
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:46,140
he had just graduated
from the police academy.

320
00:14:46,140 --> 00:14:47,630
Due to his outstanding performance,

321
00:14:47,630 --> 00:14:50,430
Leader Yao developed him
into an undercover agent

322
00:14:50,630 --> 00:14:53,290
to participate in
the 8.17 Case investigation.

323
00:14:53,410 --> 00:14:55,200
Before the operation, Leader Yao

324
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,630
gave me a note,

325
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:58,480
saying it was

326
00:14:58,680 --> 00:15:00,480
intelligence sent back by a man

327
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:01,960
codenamed Cangfeng.

328
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:03,840
We have reason to believe

329
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:05,540
that intelligence

330
00:15:05,630 --> 00:15:07,290
was sent back by Meng Junfeng.

331
00:15:08,030 --> 00:15:08,830
I suspect

332
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:11,860
he actually blew his cover very early on.

333
00:15:12,670 --> 00:15:13,870
The criminal syndicate

334
00:15:13,870 --> 00:15:15,130
took advantage of this

335
00:15:15,170 --> 00:15:17,170
and made him deliver a fake message,

336
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:18,790
which caused

337
00:15:18,790 --> 00:15:21,190
the failure of our net-closing operation.

338
00:15:24,330 --> 00:15:25,040
Sir,

339
00:15:26,750 --> 00:15:28,000
can I make a request?

340
00:15:29,270 --> 00:15:30,670
Do you have the authority

341
00:15:31,270 --> 00:15:32,930
to check if Jiang Cheng's name

342
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:35,720
is in the secret file?

343
00:15:38,670 --> 00:15:39,360
Why?

344
00:15:41,720 --> 00:15:43,440
Because that day at the water tower,

345
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,360
he told me

346
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:47,760
he knew those people
had killed my brother,

347
00:15:48,510 --> 00:15:50,840
and he had no idea
I was Zhou Jin at the time.

348
00:15:51,550 --> 00:15:53,480
He was actually saving the police.

349
00:15:55,430 --> 00:15:57,340
When you told me about Cangfeng,

350
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:59,750
I wondered if it could be him.

351
00:16:02,930 --> 00:16:04,200
Is it possible that

352
00:16:06,870 --> 00:16:08,530
he is also an undercover agent?

353
00:16:08,530 --> 00:16:09,060
Zhou Jin,

354
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:13,400
first of all, I understand how you feel,

355
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:16,090
but I have to be honest with you,

356
00:16:16,550 --> 00:16:18,410
and the truth may disappoint you.

357
00:16:20,840 --> 00:16:21,670
His name

358
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:25,280
is not in the confidential files,

359
00:16:25,280 --> 00:16:26,710
but it is

360
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:30,810
in the police fingerprint database.

361
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:32,020
The forensic examiner

362
00:16:32,020 --> 00:16:33,600
lifted a fingerprint from the gun

363
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:34,930
used to kill Leader Yao.

364
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:36,430
After comparison,

365
00:16:38,830 --> 00:16:40,690
it's Jiang Cheng's fingerprint.

366
00:17:11,119 --> 00:17:11,800
Sir,

367
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:18,460
he used to be a great cop.

368
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:20,130
I know he was once a cop,

369
00:17:20,750 --> 00:17:22,589
a good one

370
00:17:23,069 --> 00:17:24,829
with an impressive record,

371
00:17:25,270 --> 00:17:27,000
highly valued by his superiors

372
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:28,750
as a key talent.

373
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:29,750
But don't forget—

374
00:17:30,790 --> 00:17:32,150
his conduct
became completely unacceptable,

375
00:17:32,150 --> 00:17:33,480
even criminal:

376
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:35,880
hiding drugs,

377
00:17:36,180 --> 00:17:37,070
soliciting prostitutes,

378
00:17:37,070 --> 00:17:38,530
which led to a three-year prison sentence

379
00:17:38,530 --> 00:17:39,900
and ruined his career.

380
00:17:45,330 --> 00:17:47,790
Now, the criminal organization
he's part of

381
00:17:48,190 --> 00:17:50,160
is involved in organized crime,

382
00:17:50,460 --> 00:17:51,910
and he himself

383
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:54,460
is suspected of intentional homicide.

384
00:17:54,460 --> 00:17:57,520
I hope you won't let your emotions
get the better of you.

385
00:17:58,140 --> 00:17:59,340
If he contacts you,

386
00:18:00,120 --> 00:18:02,920
you must report to the team immediately.

387
00:18:04,420 --> 00:18:05,480
Do you understand?

388
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:08,410
Understood.

389
00:18:11,360 --> 00:18:11,960
Zhou Jin,

390
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:15,680
I believe you.

391
00:18:23,940 --> 00:18:24,870
Leader Yao

392
00:18:25,590 --> 00:18:26,680
and Meng Junfeng

393
00:18:27,510 --> 00:18:28,970
are missing a lot of teeth.

394
00:18:29,710 --> 00:18:31,600
During the autopsy,

395
00:18:32,190 --> 00:18:33,500
I found a large amount of
gravel and tooth fragments

396
00:18:33,500 --> 00:18:35,870
in their stomachs.

397
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:37,270
These guys

398
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:38,350
are too cruel.

399
00:18:40,610 --> 00:18:41,720
That's how he is.

400
00:18:43,300 --> 00:18:45,560
Not only does he want the police's lives,

401
00:18:45,670 --> 00:18:47,220
but he also wants to trample on

402
00:18:47,220 --> 00:18:48,680
the dignity of the police.

403
00:18:50,500 --> 00:18:51,630
Can you accurately estimate

404
00:18:51,630 --> 00:18:52,630
the time of death?

405
00:18:53,060 --> 00:18:54,060
Three days ago.

406
00:19:06,190 --> 00:19:07,110
Officer Jiang,

407
00:19:08,620 --> 00:19:10,210
does it feel frustrating

408
00:19:09,010 --> 00:19:14,470
[Day 3 after Jiang Hansheng was captured]

409
00:19:12,460 --> 00:19:14,460
to find out that you're not dead yet?

410
00:19:20,870 --> 00:19:22,590
The police will be here soon.

411
00:19:25,210 --> 00:19:26,470
I highly doubt that...

412
00:19:29,430 --> 00:19:30,590
I will kill you.

413
00:19:32,020 --> 00:19:33,700
I will definitely kill you.

414
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:39,050
Death is actually not scary.

415
00:19:42,350 --> 00:19:45,010
I wonder if Officer Jiang
has heard this saying—

416
00:19:46,550 --> 00:19:48,550
death is the true beginning

417
00:19:49,900 --> 00:19:51,340
and you will be reborn.

418
00:19:52,740 --> 00:19:53,780
Of course I know

419
00:19:55,350 --> 00:19:57,010
that you don't want to die now.

420
00:19:58,500 --> 00:19:59,830
You must be thinking

421
00:20:00,950 --> 00:20:02,460
that if you died now,

422
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:08,650
what would happen
to the girl you care about most?

423
00:20:10,970 --> 00:20:13,130
The girl in that pocket watch,

424
00:20:13,990 --> 00:20:15,320
what will happen to her?

425
00:20:56,450 --> 00:21:02,850
[Day 6 after Jiang Hansheng was captured]

426
00:21:22,060 --> 00:21:22,830
Don't touch me!

427
00:21:22,830 --> 00:21:24,350
Don't touch me! Don't come any closer!

428
00:21:24,350 --> 00:21:25,150
It's me.

429
00:21:25,170 --> 00:21:26,260
Don't touch me!

430
00:21:26,260 --> 00:21:26,830
Stay back!

431
00:21:26,830 --> 00:21:27,630
Look closely!

432
00:21:30,190 --> 00:21:30,950
It's me.

433
00:21:31,910 --> 00:21:32,590
It's me.

434
00:21:34,700 --> 00:21:35,430
Listen,

435
00:21:35,550 --> 00:21:36,680
the police are here.

436
00:21:36,710 --> 00:21:37,420
Quick.

437
00:21:38,150 --> 00:21:39,410
Help me untie the rope.

438
00:21:40,020 --> 00:21:41,150
Find a place to hide.

439
00:21:43,500 --> 00:21:44,110
Hurry!

440
00:22:02,480 --> 00:22:03,520
They're back.

441
00:22:03,720 --> 00:22:05,520
They're back.
What should we do?

442
00:22:06,150 --> 00:22:07,150
What should we do?

443
00:22:08,150 --> 00:22:09,080
Don't be afraid.

444
00:22:09,460 --> 00:22:10,260
Trust me.

445
00:22:10,460 --> 00:22:11,430
I'll get you out.

446
00:22:19,300 --> 00:22:19,890
Quick.

447
00:22:19,910 --> 00:22:20,640
Come with me.

448
00:22:35,110 --> 00:22:35,700
Get in.

449
00:22:47,260 --> 00:22:48,460
You must stay calm.

450
00:22:49,630 --> 00:22:50,690
Don't make a sound.

451
00:22:51,430 --> 00:22:52,670
I will get you out.

452
00:22:53,460 --> 00:22:54,790
Wait for me to come back.

453
00:22:55,260 --> 00:22:55,910
Don't go.

454
00:22:57,980 --> 00:22:58,630
Trust me.

455
00:22:59,980 --> 00:23:00,740
Trust me.

456
00:24:34,830 --> 00:24:35,830
Officer Jiang.

457
00:24:44,780 --> 00:24:45,390
Qi Yan,

458
00:24:47,150 --> 00:24:47,910
you lose.

459
00:24:50,460 --> 00:24:51,300
Did I?

460
00:24:55,220 --> 00:24:56,060
Don't move.

461
00:24:57,300 --> 00:24:58,300
Freeze!

462
00:25:03,300 --> 00:25:04,190
Calm down.

463
00:25:05,360 --> 00:25:07,490
I just want to return something to you.

464
00:25:16,450 --> 00:25:17,450
She's beautiful.

465
00:25:24,580 --> 00:25:26,240
Jiang Hansheng, don't shoot!

466
00:25:26,330 --> 00:25:26,890
Don't!

467
00:25:27,190 --> 00:25:28,150
I am Yao Weihai.

468
00:25:28,170 --> 00:25:29,460
Look closely, I'm Yao Weihai!

469
00:25:29,460 --> 00:25:30,020
Don't move!

470
00:25:30,020 --> 00:25:30,870
Officer Jiang.

471
00:25:30,870 --> 00:25:31,260
Calm down!

472
00:25:31,260 --> 00:25:32,420
The police are here.

473
00:25:32,420 --> 00:25:33,300
Don't get worked up.

474
00:25:33,300 --> 00:25:33,950
Listen to them.

475
00:25:33,950 --> 00:25:34,550
Calm down.

476
00:25:34,590 --> 00:25:35,590
I am Yao Weihai.

477
00:25:35,590 --> 00:25:36,780
Look closely, I am Yao Weihai.

478
00:25:36,780 --> 00:25:38,700
I just want to return something to you.

479
00:25:38,700 --> 00:25:39,220
Calm down.

480
00:25:39,220 --> 00:25:39,740
Stay calm.

481
00:25:39,740 --> 00:25:40,870
I'm Yao Weihai.

482
00:25:41,410 --> 00:25:42,150
Don't do it.

483
00:25:42,150 --> 00:25:42,550
Quick!

484
00:25:42,770 --> 00:25:43,440
Calm down!

485
00:25:43,460 --> 00:25:44,980
I'll kill you!

486
00:25:52,500 --> 00:25:53,500
I will kill you!

487
00:25:55,100 --> 00:25:55,670
Zhou Jin.

488
00:25:56,670 --> 00:25:57,670
I'll kill you!

489
00:25:58,150 --> 00:26:00,020
I will kill you!

490
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:00,910
Qi Yan!

491
00:26:01,150 --> 00:26:02,020
No!

492
00:26:41,250 --> 00:26:42,970
Officer Jiang!

493
00:27:57,230 --> 00:27:57,910
Qi Yan.

494
00:28:06,500 --> 00:28:07,740
Officer Jiang.

495
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:08,720
No.

496
00:28:09,490 --> 00:28:12,010
I should call you Professor Jiang now.

497
00:28:12,740 --> 00:28:14,000
You still remember me.

498
00:28:14,510 --> 00:28:15,440
I'm quite happy.

499
00:28:16,670 --> 00:28:17,430
How is it?

500
00:28:18,630 --> 00:28:19,780
Is my "welcome gift"

501
00:28:21,040 --> 00:28:21,990
grand enough?

502
00:28:24,780 --> 00:28:26,180
Since you don't respond,

503
00:28:27,190 --> 00:28:28,260
I'll assume you like my

504
00:28:28,260 --> 00:28:29,590
way of greeting.

505
00:28:30,390 --> 00:28:31,720
Why are you still alive?

506
00:28:35,260 --> 00:28:36,260
Professor Jiang,

507
00:28:37,910 --> 00:28:39,780
you asked the wrong question.

508
00:28:40,650 --> 00:28:41,930
You should ask

509
00:28:42,700 --> 00:28:45,060
who the person was

510
00:28:46,350 --> 00:28:48,010
you shot and killed back then?

511
00:28:49,460 --> 00:28:50,150
Who?

512
00:28:51,390 --> 00:28:52,910
If the answer were that easy to reveal,

513
00:28:52,910 --> 00:28:54,430
wouldn't it be too boring?

514
00:28:55,460 --> 00:28:56,660
Same rules as always—

515
00:28:57,700 --> 00:28:59,190
how about a game?

516
00:29:03,460 --> 00:29:04,350
Guess

517
00:29:04,740 --> 00:29:05,700
heads

518
00:29:06,260 --> 00:29:07,110
or tails.

519
00:29:07,910 --> 00:29:08,970
If you get it right,

520
00:29:10,350 --> 00:29:12,080
I'll chat with you a bit longer.

521
00:29:50,520 --> 00:29:52,320
Professor Jiang, you are a bit naughty.

522
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:53,280
Play with me.

523
00:30:35,830 --> 00:30:36,870
Professor Jiang,

524
00:30:37,430 --> 00:30:38,950
you are very impolite!

525
00:30:38,980 --> 00:30:40,790
Didn't your mother teach you?

526
00:30:41,190 --> 00:30:42,760
Politeness is the rule of communication

527
00:30:42,760 --> 00:30:43,880
between people.

528
00:30:44,540 --> 00:30:46,070
It's unnecessary with you.

529
00:30:51,060 --> 00:30:51,980
What a pity.

530
00:30:53,190 --> 00:30:54,220
I thought there was

531
00:30:54,220 --> 00:30:55,820
some connection between us.

532
00:30:56,040 --> 00:30:57,150
I thought we

533
00:30:58,470 --> 00:30:59,520
were friends.

534
00:31:01,500 --> 00:31:02,300
Right?

535
00:31:03,740 --> 00:31:04,780
I don't know why

536
00:31:04,780 --> 00:31:06,670
every time I show goodwill,

537
00:31:07,500 --> 00:31:08,780
it makes you

538
00:31:09,300 --> 00:31:10,740
hate me

539
00:31:11,540 --> 00:31:12,830
and disgusts me.

540
00:31:17,220 --> 00:31:18,590
What exactly happened?

541
00:31:25,060 --> 00:31:25,860
What's wrong?

542
00:31:28,260 --> 00:31:28,950
Hansheng.

543
00:31:30,610 --> 00:31:31,810
Is that Officer Zhou?

544
00:31:32,350 --> 00:31:33,630
Is that Officer Zhou?

545
00:31:36,280 --> 00:31:38,770
Say hello to Officer Zhou for me.

546
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:44,220
Officer Zhou.

547
00:31:45,360 --> 00:31:47,150
Who are you? What do you want?

548
00:31:47,810 --> 00:31:48,530
Zhou Jin,

549
00:31:48,910 --> 00:31:49,710
how could you?

550
00:31:49,980 --> 00:31:51,380
It's that sniper, right?

551
00:31:51,780 --> 00:31:53,430
The sniper I chased, right?

552
00:31:54,260 --> 00:31:55,720
How did he get your number?

553
00:31:56,390 --> 00:31:57,500
Why did he call you?

554
00:31:57,770 --> 00:31:58,920
Sir just told me

555
00:31:59,220 --> 00:32:00,460
there was a mole in the team.

556
00:32:00,460 --> 00:32:01,590
I didn't believe it.

557
00:32:01,910 --> 00:32:03,300
He has found you now.

558
00:32:03,740 --> 00:32:05,280
He even has found your number.

559
00:32:05,280 --> 00:32:06,410
What do they want?

560
00:32:06,740 --> 00:32:07,590
Give me the phone.

561
00:32:07,590 --> 00:32:09,590
I... I will go find Bai Yang.

562
00:32:23,780 --> 00:32:24,510
Don't worry.

563
00:32:25,500 --> 00:32:26,340
It's fine.

564
00:32:27,460 --> 00:32:28,150
I'm fine.

565
00:32:29,430 --> 00:32:30,590
Give me your phone.

566
00:32:31,670 --> 00:32:34,070
I'll ask Bai Yang
to check the phone number,

567
00:32:34,390 --> 00:32:35,150
okay?

568
00:32:38,430 --> 00:32:39,390
Don't worry.

569
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:42,060
No matter who they are,

570
00:32:43,500 --> 00:32:45,220
I will never let them hurt you.

571
00:32:48,870 --> 00:32:49,700
So,

572
00:32:51,040 --> 00:32:52,230
give me your phone.

573
00:32:53,830 --> 00:32:54,780
No need to check.

574
00:32:55,700 --> 00:32:57,020
I know who he is.

575
00:32:58,740 --> 00:32:59,620
He is Qi Yan.

576
00:33:04,410 --> 00:33:05,850
He is Qi Yan?

577
00:33:12,190 --> 00:33:13,190
Professor Jiang,

578
00:33:13,700 --> 00:33:16,020
who the person was

579
00:33:16,630 --> 00:33:18,290
you shot and killed back then?

580
00:33:18,500 --> 00:33:19,190
Hansheng.

581
00:33:20,830 --> 00:33:21,430
Hansheng.

582
00:33:23,390 --> 00:33:24,110
I'm fine.

583
00:33:25,060 --> 00:33:26,590
But if what you said is true—

584
00:33:26,980 --> 00:33:28,260
if he really is Qi Yan—

585
00:33:29,300 --> 00:33:31,700
then who was the one
that got shot back then?

586
00:33:34,700 --> 00:33:35,350
Zhou Jin,

587
00:33:36,700 --> 00:33:38,100
I need to go to Huaiguang.

588
00:33:38,800 --> 00:33:39,930
You want to look into

589
00:33:40,070 --> 00:33:42,400
the serial murder cases from 20 years ago?

590
00:33:43,540 --> 00:33:45,670
Because of some special circumstances,

591
00:33:45,670 --> 00:33:47,350
this investigation in Huaiguang

592
00:33:47,350 --> 00:33:48,610
might not go smoothly.

593
00:33:50,430 --> 00:33:51,390
If possible,

594
00:33:52,790 --> 00:33:54,470
I hope you can stay by my side.

595
00:33:54,950 --> 00:33:55,630
Of course.

596
00:33:56,870 --> 00:33:59,020
Qi Yan just asked you to send his regards;

597
00:33:59,020 --> 00:34:00,150
that's clearly a way

598
00:34:00,260 --> 00:34:02,170
to use your safety to threaten me.

599
00:34:03,280 --> 00:34:05,410
It's too dangerous for you to go alone.

600
00:34:05,460 --> 00:34:07,190
I'll go apply to Sir right away.

601
00:34:08,239 --> 00:34:10,409
Then thank you in advance, Officer Zhou.

602
00:34:10,409 --> 00:34:12,810
You must protect me
and never leave my side.

603
00:34:14,940 --> 00:34:15,670
Don't worry.

604
00:34:38,020 --> 00:34:39,219
This is the work phone

605
00:34:39,389 --> 00:34:40,800
and notebook

606
00:34:41,909 --> 00:34:43,440
that Leader Yao left for me.

607
00:34:43,469 --> 00:34:45,000
I have read them carefully.

608
00:34:45,449 --> 00:34:46,580
Based on

609
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,699
my thoughts over the past few days,

610
00:34:48,699 --> 00:34:49,820
I have 3 ideas

611
00:34:50,350 --> 00:34:51,600
I'd like to report to

612
00:34:51,639 --> 00:34:52,570
all the leaders.

613
00:34:53,320 --> 00:34:55,969
[Deputy Director Lu Zhinan,
Binjiang Provincial Public Security Bureau]

614
00:34:53,460 --> 00:34:54,179
Go ahead.

615
00:34:55,090 --> 00:34:55,739
First,

616
00:34:56,350 --> 00:34:58,020
I suspect there was an internal problem

617
00:34:58,020 --> 00:34:59,750
during the Jingang operation.

618
00:35:00,020 --> 00:35:00,870
Next,

619
00:35:01,230 --> 00:35:03,060
I will conduct an internal investigation

620
00:35:03,060 --> 00:35:03,910
to verify

621
00:35:04,220 --> 00:35:05,410
my guess.

622
00:35:05,870 --> 00:35:06,530
Meanwhile,

623
00:35:07,180 --> 00:35:08,540
I request the municipal bureau's
assistance

624
00:35:08,540 --> 00:35:09,870
in the upcoming search

625
00:35:10,140 --> 00:35:12,620
and capture operations
to enhance operational security.

626
00:35:12,620 --> 00:35:13,230
Second,

627
00:35:14,180 --> 00:35:16,510
before the Jingang operation, Leader Yao

628
00:35:16,980 --> 00:35:17,790
was already

629
00:35:18,910 --> 00:35:19,910
aware of

630
00:35:20,830 --> 00:35:22,870
the possibility of his own sacrifice.

631
00:35:22,870 --> 00:35:23,460
However,

632
00:35:24,180 --> 00:35:25,660
having worked with him

633
00:35:25,660 --> 00:35:26,750
for so long,

634
00:35:27,100 --> 00:35:28,870
I know he wouldn't allow himself

635
00:35:28,870 --> 00:35:31,530
and Cangfeng
to be sacrificed without purpose.

636
00:35:31,980 --> 00:35:34,040
Therefore, there's
definitely more complexity

637
00:35:34,040 --> 00:35:36,570
behind this case
than we initially imagined.

638
00:35:36,910 --> 00:35:37,660
Here,

639
00:35:38,870 --> 00:35:39,870
I'd like to follow

640
00:35:40,580 --> 00:35:42,440
Leader Yao's final instructions

641
00:35:42,580 --> 00:35:44,310
and shoulder the burden of

642
00:35:44,310 --> 00:35:46,110
the 8/17 Case and related cases.

643
00:35:47,310 --> 00:35:48,750
Leaders, please trust me

644
00:35:49,590 --> 00:35:50,920
and give me this chance.

645
00:35:52,310 --> 00:35:53,390
I will consider

646
00:35:54,830 --> 00:35:56,160
this matter carefully.

647
00:35:56,390 --> 00:35:58,020
Tell me your third point first.

648
00:35:58,020 --> 00:36:00,020
The third point is about Jiang Cheng.

649
00:36:00,020 --> 00:36:01,310
Don't jump to conclusions too early

650
00:36:01,310 --> 00:36:02,620
about whether he is a friend or a foe,

651
00:36:02,620 --> 00:36:04,180
dead or alive.

652
00:36:04,980 --> 00:36:05,750
I believe

653
00:36:06,580 --> 00:36:07,980
the fingerprints on the gun

654
00:36:07,980 --> 00:36:09,540
were left in a deliberately obvious way.

655
00:36:09,540 --> 00:36:11,200
The more deliberate it seems,

656
00:36:11,350 --> 00:36:13,710
the more it suggests
countless possibilities.

657
00:36:13,710 --> 00:36:14,950
Therefore, we should treat him

658
00:36:14,950 --> 00:36:16,020
with the same seriousness

659
00:36:16,020 --> 00:36:17,180
as we do Old Scorpion,

660
00:36:17,180 --> 00:36:18,060
Qi Yan,

661
00:36:18,210 --> 00:36:19,440
and

662
00:36:20,460 --> 00:36:21,350
He Wu.

663
00:36:22,110 --> 00:36:26,460
[Huaiguang City]

664
00:36:32,790 --> 00:36:34,180
I went down to the county for a visit,

665
00:36:34,180 --> 00:36:35,180
so I'm not around.

666
00:36:35,230 --> 00:36:36,890
You're already in Huaiguang?

667
00:36:37,100 --> 00:36:38,790
We're already in Xiacheng District.

668
00:36:38,790 --> 00:36:39,440
Alright then.

669
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,910
Find a place to stay first.

670
00:36:40,980 --> 00:36:41,430
Okay.

671
00:36:47,950 --> 00:36:49,280
Prof went to the county.

672
00:36:49,660 --> 00:36:51,660
Mr. Wang went to the county himself?

673
00:36:53,060 --> 00:36:54,180
We can go to

674
00:36:54,180 --> 00:36:55,580
the Xiacheng Branch first.

675
00:36:55,580 --> 00:36:56,100
Perfect.

676
00:36:56,100 --> 00:36:56,910
The hotel I booked

677
00:36:56,910 --> 00:36:58,970
is very close to the Xiacheng Branch.

678
00:36:59,100 --> 00:37:00,540
And looking at the pictures,

679
00:37:00,540 --> 00:37:02,000
it should be pretty clean.

680
00:37:03,310 --> 00:37:04,510
As long as it's clean.

681
00:37:07,060 --> 00:37:08,720
So how many rooms did you book?

682
00:37:10,510 --> 00:37:11,110
One.

683
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:12,290
Let's go.

684
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:24,010
It doesn't look

685
00:37:24,120 --> 00:37:25,690
as clean as in the photos.

686
00:37:26,500 --> 00:37:27,360
It's fine by me.

687
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:48,110
Is it okay?

688
00:37:52,550 --> 00:37:53,110
Okay.

689
00:37:57,180 --> 00:37:59,270
Although he is unreachable
from time to time,

690
00:37:59,270 --> 00:38:00,910
there is definitely a problem this time.

691
00:38:00,910 --> 00:38:02,770
Moving his grandparents' graves

692
00:38:02,980 --> 00:38:04,230
was decided half a year ago.

693
00:38:04,230 --> 00:38:05,100
It's a big deal.

694
00:38:05,500 --> 00:38:06,950
Isn't it abnormal

695
00:38:07,180 --> 00:38:09,510
that he couldn't be found
on the exact day?

696
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:18,150
[Did Jiang Cheng ask you to do it for him?
Did he call you about the money?]

697
00:38:22,870 --> 00:38:24,020
Nothing at all.

698
00:38:24,460 --> 00:38:26,190
That's why I said he is missing.

699
00:38:26,710 --> 00:38:28,640
His phone is off,
and he's not replying to messages.

700
00:38:28,640 --> 00:38:29,710
I've been looking for him for 3 or 4 days.

701
00:38:29,710 --> 00:38:32,510
I'm telling you,
something definitely happened.

702
00:38:45,520 --> 00:38:47,810
[He'll reply if he wants to contact you.
Listen to me. Stop looking for him.].

703
00:38:58,750 --> 00:38:59,810
What's the matter?

704
00:39:03,060 --> 00:39:04,390
Jiang Cheng is missing.

705
00:39:05,140 --> 00:39:06,470
Yan Bin is very worried.

706
00:39:07,660 --> 00:39:10,860
You didn't say anything to him
about Jiang Cheng, did you?

707
00:39:15,750 --> 00:39:16,620
Do you think

708
00:39:18,830 --> 00:39:19,710
a person

709
00:39:19,850 --> 00:39:20,350
can really

710
00:39:20,350 --> 00:39:21,950
change that drastically?

711
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:28,000
Humans are creatures of circumstance.

712
00:39:28,580 --> 00:39:29,500
Back then,

713
00:39:30,870 --> 00:39:32,470
I always thought Jiang Cheng

714
00:39:33,580 --> 00:39:34,710
was a kind,

715
00:39:35,330 --> 00:39:36,120
upright man.

716
00:39:44,580 --> 00:39:46,310
To have faith in the one you love

717
00:39:46,430 --> 00:39:47,160
is not wrong.

718
00:39:55,540 --> 00:39:56,200
I loved him,

719
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:57,930
but it's in the past.

720
00:39:59,370 --> 00:40:00,700
We are police officers.

721
00:40:01,270 --> 00:40:02,060
Everything

722
00:40:03,040 --> 00:40:04,240
depends on evidence.

723
00:40:50,500 --> 00:40:51,230
Jiang Cheng,

724
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:53,040
give me your hands.

725
00:40:53,350 --> 00:40:54,350
What is this for?

726
00:40:55,350 --> 00:40:56,150
It's the rule.

727
00:40:56,380 --> 00:40:57,310
Always has been.

728
00:41:04,100 --> 00:41:05,760
Be gentle. It hurts, Zhou Jin.

729
00:41:09,060 --> 00:41:09,870
Also,

730
00:41:11,310 --> 00:41:13,110
your eyes need to be blindfolded.

731
00:41:13,110 --> 00:41:14,440
No need to gag me, right?

732
00:41:28,300 --> 00:41:28,870
Done.

733
00:41:31,420 --> 00:41:32,620
You are quite strong.

734
00:42:00,450 --> 00:42:01,850
Why aren't they back yet?

735
00:42:03,790 --> 00:42:04,750
It's already nice of them

736
00:42:04,750 --> 00:42:06,150
to make us two cups of tea.

737
00:42:07,470 --> 00:42:08,930
Are they really that busy?

738
00:42:09,390 --> 00:42:10,140
I'll go ask.

739
00:42:10,510 --> 00:42:11,240
Zhou Jin,

740
00:42:11,500 --> 00:42:12,230
don't.

741
00:42:12,750 --> 00:42:14,080
Even if we're with Prof,

742
00:42:14,350 --> 00:42:15,150
it's the same.

743
00:42:16,660 --> 00:42:17,580
Why?

744
00:42:19,180 --> 00:42:19,980
No matter what,

745
00:42:19,980 --> 00:42:21,270
we are colleagues.

746
00:42:21,510 --> 00:42:23,240
I didn't expect a warm welcome,

747
00:42:23,690 --> 00:42:24,890
but this attitude...

748
00:42:28,830 --> 00:42:29,500
Captain Li.

749
00:42:30,660 --> 00:42:31,750
It really is you.

750
00:42:32,950 --> 00:42:35,130
Wang Pengze left and now you're here.

751
00:42:35,380 --> 00:42:36,010
What?

752
00:42:36,180 --> 00:42:37,180
A revolving door?

753
00:42:37,590 --> 00:42:38,140
Wait,

754
00:42:38,390 --> 00:42:40,030
do you not trust us,

755
00:42:40,130 --> 00:42:41,390
or don't you trust him?

756
00:42:42,520 --> 00:42:43,210
Hello,

757
00:42:43,540 --> 00:42:44,790
a comrade earlier

758
00:42:44,810 --> 00:42:45,910
said he would help us find

759
00:42:45,910 --> 00:42:47,940
the files for the 1997 serial killer case.

760
00:42:47,940 --> 00:42:50,020
But he's been gone for over an hour

761
00:42:50,270 --> 00:42:51,430
and hasn't returned.

762
00:42:51,430 --> 00:42:52,270
Just wait.

763
00:42:52,630 --> 00:42:55,230
This case has gone
back and forth so many times,

764
00:42:55,540 --> 00:42:56,590
there's a ton of material.

765
00:42:56,590 --> 00:42:57,990
We won't bother you then.

766
00:42:58,420 --> 00:42:59,110
Let's go.

767
00:42:59,790 --> 00:43:00,620
Go?
